metadata.description: In this tribute to the legacy of Kobe Bryant, contemporary street artist Seek One stays true to his signature one of one fashion, but with the addition of an NFT to form a fully hybrid piece. As the featured artist behind the web3 project Chosen Ones, Seek One heavily contributes to the web3 world; however, in combining his passion for in pop culture and iconic portraits with his work in web3, this Seek One exclusive pushes his web3 expression into another dimension.
